# Routed six-row-matrix manifest (repo-root-relative paths, one per line).
#
# Every file listed here MUST contain all six read-path routing rows enforced by
# scripts/check-routed-test-rows.sh (api-happy-path, api-cache-not-live,
# api-500-fallback, api-404-error, controller-down, escape-hatch).
#
# This checked-in denominator is the hardening the CLI-unification council asked
# for: without it, renaming a row marker would drop every file to "0 rows found"
# and the guard would pass vacuously, silently unpoliced. With it, the same
# rename makes every manifest file report <6 rows and the check fails loudly.
#
# When a command becomes a fully-migrated read-path matrix file (all six rows),
# add it here; the check fails if a fully-covered cmd_*_test.go is NOT listed.
cmd/gc/cmd_beads_test.go
cmd/gc/cmd_citystatus_test.go
cmd/gc/cmd_convoy_test.go
cmd/gc/cmd_mail_test.go
cmd/gc/cmd_maintenance_test.go
cmd/gc/cmd_order_test.go
cmd/gc/cmd_rig_test.go
cmd/gc/cmd_session_test.go
